Adding User to the sudo Group!
sudo -aG sudo uesrname

To install debian pakage:
sudo dpkg -i code_1.57.1-1623937013_amd64.deb 

To secure copy files to remote server:
scp -r (directoryname) distitation x@xxxxx:/home/x    This one is for a directory
scp test.txt user@192.168.100.44:/home/user           This one is for files
To check if installed the package in Debian.
dpkg -l ecryptfs*
